{"tha-ap123:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap123:0.2":"Sereyyavagga ","tha-ap123:0.3":"Sereyyakattheraapadana ","tha-ap123:1.1":"â€œAjjhayako mantadharo, ","tha-ap123:1.2":"tinnam vedana paragu; ","tha-ap123:1.3":"Abbhokase thito santo, ","tha-ap123:1.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap123:2.1":"Siham yatha vanacaram, ","tha-ap123:2.2":"byaggharajamva nittasam; ","tha-ap123:2.3":"Tidhapabhinnamatangam, ","tha-ap123:2.4":"kunjaramva mahesinam. ","tha-ap123:3.1":"Sereyyakam gahetvana, ","tha-ap123:3.2":"akase ukkhipim aham; ","tha-ap123:3.3":"Buddhassa anubhavena, ","tha-ap123:3.4":"parivarenti sabbaso. ","tha-ap123:4.1":"Adhitthahi mahaviro, ","tha-ap123:4.2":"sabbannu lokanayako; ","tha-ap123:4.3":"Samanta pupphacchadana, ","tha-ap123:4.4":"okirimsu narasabham. ","tha-ap123:5.1":"Tato sa pupphakancuka, ","tha-ap123:5.2":"antovanta bahimukha; ","tha-ap123:5.3":"Sattaham chadanam katva, ","tha-ap123:5.4":"tato antaradhayatha. ","tha-ap123:6.1":"Tanca acchariyam disva, ","tha-ap123:6.2":"abbhutam lomahamsanam; ","tha-ap123:6.3":"Buddhe cittam pasadesim, ","tha-ap123:6.4":"sugate lokanayake. ","tha-ap123:7.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap123:7.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap123:7.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap123:7.4":"duggatim nupapajjaham. ","tha-ap123:8.1":"Pannarasasahassamhi, ","tha-ap123:8.2":"kappanam pancavisati; ","tha-ap123:8.3":"Vitamala samana ca, ","tha-ap123:8.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap123:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap123:9.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap123:9.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap123:9.4":"katam buddhassa sasanamâ€. ","tha-ap123:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sereyyako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap123:11.1":"Sereyyakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}